  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Educate Girls and Orphans in rural Uganda</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">There are millions of children living in extreme poverty in rural Uganda. They are mainly from poor farming communities that cannot afford basic needs. Girls, orphans and disabled children are most at risk. They lack access to education, basic healthcare, food and other basic needs. This exposes them to abject poverty, violence, abuse and forced marriages. We can stop this from happening by providing their school fees, basic healthcare, food, clean water, uniform and basic needs.</narrative>
  </description>
